8#ifndef SRC_SIMPLE_TAG_PARSER_H_
9#define SRC_SIMPLE_TAG_PARSER_H_
10
11#include "src/bool_parser.h"
12#include "src/byte_parser.h"
13#include "src/master_value_parser.h"
14#include "webm/dom_types.h"
15#include "webm/id.h"
16
17namespace webm {
18
19// Spec reference:
20// http://matroska.org/technical/specs/index.html#SimpleTag
21// http://www.webmproject.org/docs/container/#SimpleTag
22class SimpleTagParser : public MasterValueParser<SimpleTag> {
23 public:
24 SimpleTagParser(std::size_t max_recursive_depth = 25)
25 : MasterValueParser<SimpleTag>(
26 MakeChild<StringParser>(Id::kTagName, &SimpleTag::name),
27 MakeChild<StringParser>(Id::kTagLanguage, &SimpleTag::language),
28 MakeChild<BoolParser>(Id::kTagDefault, &SimpleTag::is_default),
29 MakeChild<StringParser>(Id::kTagString, &SimpleTag::string),
30 MakeChild<BinaryParser>(Id::kTagBinary, &SimpleTag::binary),
31 MakeChild<SimpleTagParser>(Id::kSimpleTag, &SimpleTag::tags,
32 max_recursive_depth)) {}
33};
34
35} // namespace webm
36
37#endif // SRC_SIMPLE_TAG_PARSER_H_
